fields.description: The group id from the provider of resource the shared private link resource is for.
fields.name: GroupId

fields.description: The resource id of the resource the shared private link resource is for.
fields.name: PrivateLinkResourceId

fields.description: The provisioning state of the shared private link resource. Valid values are Updating, Deleting, Failed, Succeeded or Incomplete.
fields.name: ProvisioningState

fields.description: The request message for requesting approval of the shared private link resource.
fields.name: RequestMessage

fields.description: Optional. Can be used to specify the Azure Resource Manager location of the resource to which a shared private link is to be created. This is only required for those resources whose DNS configuration are regional (such as Azure Kubernetes Service).
fields.name: ResourceRegion

fields.description: Status of the shared private link resource. Valid values are Pending, Approved, Rejected or Disconnected.
fields.name: Status
